    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214571>
    dc:description "FIGURES 37 – 42. Sclerotized parts of Tereancistrum arcuatus sp. n. from the dourado, Salminus brasiliensis, from Paraná River, Brazil. 37. Copulatory complex (ventral view). 38. Hook. 39. Ventral anchor. 40. Dorsal anchor. 41. Ven t ral bar. 42. Dorsal bar. All figures are drawn to the 50 µm scale, except fig. 38 (10 µm scale)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214571/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

